{"tid":2454453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"哥哥忌辰舉行網上音樂會 唐唐親自命名《想你‧張國榮》緬懷","createTime":"2021-03-20T09:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T09:51:48.000Z","uid":335664,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f877402c2c0fb6dc7fe18c4a6102f080ff75c461","tid":2454453,"uid":335664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:02:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrncmGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrncmGE.jpg&h=5fdfd422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n製作人蕭潮順繼去年疫情先後舉辦許冠傑、郭富城網上直播音樂會，為香港人打氣。經過一年多時間抗疫，香港疫情仍未減退，因此蕭潮順今年將於4月1日哥哥張國榮忌辰當日，舉行名為《想你‧張國榮》網上音樂會。<br />\n<br />\n不經不覺，哥哥張國榮離逝已經18年，蕭潮順有感過去一年香港的疫情，確診數字仍起起跌跌，不單止影響大家工作、生活及心情，就連入場看演唱會、話劇甚至睇電影減壓，都因限聚令而隨時被迫暫停，因此他與鄭丹瑞的《健康‧旦》再次製作一小時的網上音樂會作全球直播，希望再一次為大家打氣，藉着香港人熟悉的哥哥歌曲為大家帶來正能量。<br />\n對於再次搞抗疫網上音樂會為大家打氣，蕭潮順向《蘋果》表示︰「呢個就係我哋嘅原意，都係呢幾日決定做，我哋就即刻去搵陳太（陳淑芬）同唐唐（唐鶴德），一定要攞到佢哋嘅批准。有呢件事之後，我哋就透過陳太問唐唐，佢好快OK咗，仲幫我哋度埋個名叫《想你‧張國榮》畀我哋，而家我哋搵緊歌手。今次都係喺尖沙嘴海運大廈天台上面做，個景又靚，我好有信心比上兩次做得更加好。」<br />\n<br />\n哥哥張國榮於2003年4月1日離逝，當年香港同樣遇上沙士疫情。而蕭潮順和鄭旦瑞的《健康‧旦》於去年疫情下，先後於4月舉行《2020許冠傑同舟共濟Online Concert》，以及5月舉行《郭富城鼓舞‧動起來網上慈善演唱會》為業界籌款和香港人打氣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210318/E43B63L3NBEINNNKKYGLS7PVZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210318%2FE43B63L3NBEINNNKKYGLS7PVZY%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=05c83120\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210318%2FE43B63L3NBEINNNKKYGLS7PVZY%2F&h=ce69a7ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210318/E43B63L3NBEINNNKKYGLS7PVZY/</a>"},{"pid":"2f3941a8b65184245696c6e1ea4372c7f64f3d2e","tid":2454453,"uid":1426,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"還我4月1日愚人節，不是基佬榮自殺紀念日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2438632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2438632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"80e1782eccefaadf08cf3332875b38f6aa91b659","tid":2454453,"uid":335664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f3941a8b65184245696c6e1ea4372c7f64f3d2e","tid":2454453,"uid":1426,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"還我4月1日愚人節，不是基佬榮自殺紀念日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2438632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2438632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"75276bc11c563311d5fd32b55ff0ff3d26399ba1","tid":2454453,"uid":525,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"80e1782eccefaadf08cf3332875b38f6aa91b659","tid":2454453,"uid":335664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2f3941a8b65184245696c6e1ea4372c7f64f3d2e","tid":2454453,"uid":1426,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"還我4月1日愚人節，不是基佬榮自殺紀念日！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2438632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2438632</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:05:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"死基佬咪煩啦<br />\n比你屌都屌唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be7ac5cec038fd5d0de82bae94f04c8f210dbfc3","tid":2454453,"uid":1426,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"唔願愛妹妹個蓮<br />\n唯一喜歡咬鞭<br />\n<br />\n你個春袋 我個春袋<br />\n互咬先至係甜"},{"pid":"7bbc070f1c404c42d217d78889ca7a1ac0f03efb","tid":2454453,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:14:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D6lZcpH34ww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD6lZcpH34ww&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=3a2cdb59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D6lZcpH34ww</a>"},{"pid":"9125cba3e4d5e35cdc9157cda4e350f2a06eb04f","tid":2454453,"ui